First: Try to run game through file manager or manually generate run configuration for Game class main
Add the following VM options: --module-path /usr/share/openjfx/lib --add-modules javafx.controls,javafx.fxml

If the project SDK is not setup: Set project SDK to Java version 17.0.9 (ideally), at least 16

If javaFX required component do not load, add them as a dependency through the project structure

If classes are having trouble accessing each-other, RepairIDE through file tab and click Rescan Project Indexes

If java language level does not match: set language level to 16, records are used in project